des:
This Skill provides the details of my cab timings on all the days and across all the time i.e. Morning, afternoon, evening and night.

Since I work on shifts this has been enabled and my shift changes daily and it is easier with this skill to track my cab details.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
